      "updated": 1776999508058,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Queue w/ CPU priority sort\n───────────\nstd::sort  (introsort,  O(n log n))\nBuffer: per-scenario\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nmeasured sort time\n45 µs (low) -> 4 222 µs (high)\nScales with batch size",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Queue w/ CPU priority sort\n───────────\nstd::sort  (introsort,  O(n log n))\nBuffer: per-scenario\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nmeasured sort time\n45 µs (low) -> 4 222 µs (high)\nScales with batch size",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "ac",
      "autoResize": true
    },
