      "updated": 1776999515894,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Queue w/ GPU priority sort\n───────────\nThrust radix sort  (CUDA,  O(d·n))\nBuffer: per-scenario\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nGPU kernel time\n34 µs (low) -> 70 µs (high)\nStays flat with batch size\nPinned memory\n(cudaHostAlloc)\nPipeline parallelism\n(3 async CUDA streams)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Queue w/ GPU priority sort\n───────────\nThrust radix sort  (CUDA,  O(d·n))\nBuffer: per-scenario\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nGPU kernel time\n34 µs (low) -> 70 µs (high)\nStays flat with batch size\nPinned memory\n(cudaHostAlloc)\nPipeline parallelism\n(3 async CUDA streams)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "ae",
      "autoResize": true
    },
